<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink135">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>paitala mallēm pāṇa paṇaittō</l>
<l>ḷaitamain takaṉṟa valku</l>
<l>ṉeytalaṅ kaṇṇiyai nērtaṉām peṟiṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh bard, we will not have sadness</l>
    <l>If we obtain a meeting with the young lady of the Neytal [region]</l>
      <l>With bamboo-shoulders [and] wonderful, fitted, wide hips.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
